      Adding a Station Port Configuration (cont'd)
      ============================================
      If the station port does not exist, the Add a Station Port screen
      will be displayed, requiring the station port configuration to be input.
      The program will display the valid data ranges for each field, and
      if an invalid value is input, an error message will be displayed,
      and you will be required to input the parameter again. NOTE: if
      you enter "E" while adding, the menu will be displayed and the ADD
      will not be performed!
 
      Modifying a Station Port Configuration
      ======================================
      To modify a configuration, enter "2" (for Modify Station Configuration),
      and press return.  The program will then prompt for the station number
      and then the port number.  If the station port does not exist,
      an error message will be displayed, and you will be prompted for
      another station.  If the configuration exists, the Modify a Port
 
 
