      Deleting a Station Class
      ========================
      This option will allow a station port config to be deleted.
      Before performing this option, you should ensure that no stations
      will be effected by deleting this configuration from the database.
      To delete a configuration, enter "3" and press return.  Enter the
      station and port number, and if it exists, the Delete a Station
      Port Configuration screen will be displayed.
      If the record does not exist, an error message will be displayed, and
      you must re-enter the number.  Once the Delete Screen has been
      displayed, look at the configuration information to ensure that this
      is the correct class.  If you wish to delete it, enter "Y" and press
      return, and a message will be displayed informing that the record
      was deleted.  If you no not wish to delete the record, enter "N" and
      the configuration will not be deleted.
 
 
 
