      Listing Station Port Configurations
      ===================================
      This option will allow all station port configurations to be
      displayed.  The user also has the ability to scroll forward or back,
      to view the desired information.
 
      For more information refer to Station Class Listing help.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
